---
title: Premium Fillet Steak & Chive Sauce with Parmesan Mash & Sautéed Greens
description: Make a flavour-packed sauce to drizzle over a tender cut of premium fillet steak using onion, chives and garlic. Then, finish off
your gourmet creation with creamy mash and vibrant greens.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/premium-fillet-steak-tarragon-sauce-48093595.jpg
